com.googlecode.jsendnsca.builders
Class NagiosSettingsBuilder

java.lang.Object
  com.googlecode.jsendnsca.builders.NagiosSettingsBuilder

public class NagiosSettingsBuilder
extends Object

Used to construct a NagiosSettings instance using a builder pattern e.g. 

 
 final NagiosSettings nagiosSettings = new NagiosSettingsBuilder().withNagiosHost(HOSTNAME).withPassword(PASSWORD).create();

Since:
1.2
Author:
Raj.Patel
